Anyway, I had a crazy little thought/idea. One small problem with the list is that you cant prove that you have a pearl, we have to take your word for it, till we find out otherwise. (Ixiblat raids tend to get noticed) Well, someone mentioned an idea which would prove you have a pearl. (Or, prove it as much as we are able to) People could right-click their pearl to get the stats (and thus the name of the item as well), and while that screen's up, screenshot their pearl, with their name somewhere on the screen as well, and either post it or email it somewhere. Problem with this though, is I dont believe it would be easy to get everyone to participate in this, and there'd need to be some help for the techie-challenged. (How to post screenshots, or how to convert a picture to anything but those huge awful .bmp's before emailing them somewhere).<br>
<br>
Any thoughts on this? I'm just tossing out an idea, nothing more. ; ) <p>Cayleu Starshine
